NK014(pha)012:0: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i gzhal med khang gi rnam par
NK014(pha)012:1: bzhag pa gsal ba'i sgron me'i rtsa ba bzhugs so
NK014(pha)012:3: rigs rnams kun gyi bdag po mchog /
NK014(pha)012:4: sangs rgyas kun gyi spyi gzugs can //
NK014(pha)012:5: drug pa kun tu bzang po dang //
NK014(pha)012:6: dbyer med kun mkhyen bla ma la //
NK014(pha)012:7: dngos po kun gyi phyag btsal nas //
NK014(pha)012:8: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK014(pha)012:9: bsgom bya bzhin du bzhengs pa'i tshul //
NK014(pha)012:10: mtshungs med bla ma'i gsung bzhin bri //
NK014(pha)012:13: khog yug 1me gur cha chen gcig /
NK014(pha)012:14: de phyed rdo rje rwa ba'i nang //
NK014(pha)012:16: cha chen phyed dor zlum po ru //
NK014(pha)012:17: bskor ba pad+ma'i lte ba'i mthar //
NK014(pha)012:18: cha phran gnyis pa'i 'dab mas bskor //
NK014(pha)012:19: de steng pad lte dang mnyam pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:20: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang //
NK014(pha)012:21: rtsibs brten mu khyud ldan pa ste //
NK014(pha)012:22: 'di'i dpangs cha chen gcig yin rdo rje sngon po 'greng bu grangs med kyis yar spags pa'o //
NK014(pha)012:23: rgyud dang man ngag gzhan phal mo che ba la ni sna tshogs rdo rjer bzhed //
NK014(pha)012:24: logs 3ni dbus nas cha chen bzhi //
NK014(pha)012:25: dor ba'i phyi rol rtsig pa ni //
NK014(pha)012:26: dpangs su cha bran bcu gsum ste //
NK014(pha)012:27: cha bran gcig zheng lnga sbrags so //
NK014(pha)012:28: de yi rtsa bar 'dod yon gyi //
NK014(pha)012:29: zur bzhi dang dbus brgyad la zla phyed rdo rjes mtshan pa bcu gnyis kyis brgyan /
NK014(pha)012:30: snam bu zheng dang dpangs gnyis kar //
NK014(pha)012:31: cha cha na phyed re sgo khyud kyi //
NK014(pha)012:32: rtsig pa'i phyi la thug pas bskor //
NK014(pha)012:33: rtsig steng ser po phra can rin chen pha gu ni //
NK014(pha)012:34: cha phran gcig dpangs zheng phyed gnyis //
NK014(pha)012:35: phyed po rtsig pa'i phyir 'phyang ba //
NK014(pha)012:36: de nyid 'degs byed seng mgo yi //
NK014(pha)012:37: kha nas mu tig do shal 'phyang //
NK014(pha)012:38: pha gu'i steng du bre spungs dpangs //
NK014(pha)012:39: cha phran phyed dang gnyis pa ste //
NK014(pha)012:40: yang na ka thung cha phran gcig /
NK014(pha)012:41: gzhu la cha phran phyed pa'o //
NK014(pha)012:42: bre dmar spungs dang ka ba gang byed kyang //
NK014(pha)012:43: zur du re re phyogs bzhi por //
NK014(pha)012:44: gsum gsum khyon dril bcu drug go //
NK014(pha)012:45: de steng gdung leb brtsig mtha' dang //
NK014(pha)012:46: khad mnyam zheng du cha bran gcig /
NK014(pha)012:47: dpangs su cha bran phyed pas 'gebs //
NK014(pha)012:48: phyogs mdog gdung ste phyam nyer brgyad gyi tshad dpangs la //
NK014(pha)012:49: cha phran phyed dang gdung phyir yang //
NK014(pha)012:50: de tsam 'phyar sne tsi pa tra'i //
NK014(pha)012:51: kha nas rin chen d+r+wa ba dang //
NK014(pha)012:52: d+r+wa ba phyed sne la dril chung dang nyi zla nor bu sogs rlung bskyod can /
NK014(pha)012:54: de nyid nang du mi 'phos pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:55: thabs su gdung dang gzhu'i ngos la //
NK014(pha)012:56: gzer btab gser skud bzhi po sbrags //
NK014(pha)012:57: phyam steng cha chung gcig tsam pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:58: dpangs la bgos pa'i byi rtse dang //
NK014(pha)012:60: phyi mtha'i kha da chad du bya //
NK014(pha)012:62: cha phran dkar po chu bum thur bstan lta bu /
NK014(pha)012:64: thog steng pu shud dkar po la dmar po'i pu shud dod pa /
NK014(pha)012:66: rtsig pa'i drang thad bslang ba'o //
NK014(pha)012:68: btegs pa'i ka thung cha phran gsum re'i steng du /
NK014(pha)012:70: gdung leb steng gi phyam bkal te //
NK014(pha)012:71: g.yab sgor tshul du phyam gyi thog /
NK014(pha)012:73: khyams kyi sa rin chen sna tshogs /
NK014(pha)012:75: cha bran gcig gis mtho bar bya //
NK014(pha)012:76: khyams zheng cha bran gsum pa'i nang //
NK014(pha)012:78: de nang mu khyud rdor phreng dang //
NK014(pha)012:79: rtsibs bzhi lte bar bcas par bya //
NK014(pha)012:80: gru chad rdor phreng rtsibs lte ba //
NK014(pha)012:81: rim par cha phran re re spags //
NK014(pha)012:82: glo 'bur gru chad las thig gang //
NK014(pha)012:83: matho'o rtsibs mchan rdor phreng las //
NK014(pha)012:84: de tsam dma' bar byas na mdzes //
NK014(pha)012:85: thog 'bubs bar pa gdung zlum steng //
NK014(pha)012:86: bum pa'i rtsig dpangs cha phran bdun //
NK014(pha)012:88: lto ba'i tshul ni cha chen gcig phyir gyes pa lta bu /
NK014(pha)012:89: cha phran bar nang du rgyu ba lta bu'o //
NK014(pha)012:90: de steng gdung zlum cha phyed 'gebs //
NK014(pha)012:91: nang gi rdor phreng la brten pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:92: gzhu dang ka gdan bcas pa'i dpangs //
NK014(pha)012:93: cha bran nyi shu rtsa gcig re //
NK014(pha)012:94: yod pa'i ka ba phyogs re rer //
NK014(pha)012:95: gnyis gnyis brgyad phyogs mdog rin po che las grub pa /
NK014(pha)012:97: dpangs su cha bran phyed ldan pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:98: rdo rje'i tal gdung bzhis rgyug pas //
NK014(pha)012:99: mig mngas ris su bris pa'i sne //
NK014(pha)012:100: gdung zlum steng du khel bar bya //
NK014(pha)012:101: de steng cha chung gcig dpangs la //
NK014(pha)012:102: bgos pa'i phyam rtsa nyer brgyad dang //
NK014(pha)012:103: bya 'dab zlum po phyogs bzhir drug re mtshams bzhir re re /
NK014(pha)012:104: phyi khyams sne rnams tsi pa tra'i kha nas d+r+wa
NK014(pha)012:105: ba dang d+r+wa phyed 'phyang bas bum lto khebs pa'o
NK014(pha)012:107: cha chung gnyis pa'i 'phyar ldan pas //
NK014(pha)012:108: re mig dbus ma ma gtogs spang leb dang thog sas brdal /
NK014(pha)012:109: mthar rgya phub dang pu shu gnyis gru bzhi'i tshul du bskor dgos /
NK014(pha)012:111: dbus kyi mthong kha gru bzhi pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:112: zur bzhir ka gdung gzhu bcas dpangs //
NK014(pha)012:113: cha chen gcig go phyogs bzhi la skar khung bzhi /
NK014(pha)012:115: gdung la cha bran phyed yin te //
NK014(pha)012:116: rgya phub cha phran gcig pa'o //
NK014(pha)012:117: de steng pad+ma cha phran gcig /
NK014(pha)012:118: chos 'khor bcu gsum char khebs bcas //
NK014(pha)012:119: bsdoms pa'i dpangs la cha chen gnyis //
NK014(pha)012:120: rtse mor sgyu 'phrul zhi ba la /
NK014(pha)012:122: tog dpangs cha phran phyed bdun no //
NK014(pha)012:123: sgo ni phyogs 5bzhi'i rtsig pa'i dbus //
NK014(pha)012:124: cha chen gcig pa'i sgo bya ste //
NK014(pha)012:125: mdun du sgo khyud sgo yi tshad //
NK014(pha)012:126: de yi g.yas g.yon sgo'i phyed re //
NK014(pha)012:128: de mdun de mnyam sgo logs 'then //
NK014(pha)012:129: sgo dang khyud 'gram logs bzhi ka /
NK014(pha)012:130: dpangs su cha chen phyed gsum dang //
NK014(pha)012:131: cha chung gcig gi sum gnyis ldan //
NK014(pha)012:132: sgo logs mtha' yi rtsig mtshams nas //
NK014(pha)012:133: nang thad cha phran phyed gnyis re //
NK014(pha)012:134: gzhal mtshams cha chung phyed pa yi //
NK014(pha)012:135: zheng ldan ka ba dpangs cha bran //
NK014(pha)012:136: phyed brgyad ldan pas btegs pa yi //
NK014(pha)012:137: cha bran phyed pa'i gdung ma gtod //
NK014(pha)012:138: de steng ka thog ka bzhag gis //
NK014(pha)012:139: ka thung dpangs su cha chung ni //
NK014(pha)012:140: phyed gnyis kyis btegs sngar 'dra yi //
NK014(pha)012:141: gdung bkal de steng sgo logs nas //
NK014(pha)012:143: ka thung bar stong gsum po der //
NK014(pha)012:144: g.yas g.yon gsum gsum dbus su lnga'i //
NK014(pha)012:145: bcu gcig rdo rje'i d+r+wa mig bya //
NK014(pha)012:146: rtsa thig dang ni sgo khyud gnyis //
NK014(pha)012:147: phrad mtshams g.yas g.yon cha chung phyed //
NK014(pha)012:148: steng 'og cha phran re re yi //
NK014(pha)012:149: ru bzhi'i dbus su sgo glegs ni //
NK014(pha)012:150: cha phran bdun dpangs nyis ral 'dzugs //
NK014(pha)012:152: rgyu yi rta babs them skas te //
NK014(pha)012:153: sgo khang phyi ma las nang ma //
NK014(pha)012:154: cha chung gcig gis spags pa la //
NK014(pha)012:155: phyi yi them skas bzhi po 'dzugs //
NK014(pha)012:156: sgo khang nang ma las kyang khyams //
NK014(pha)012:157: mtho ba de mnyam them pa yi //
NK014(pha)012:158: 'og tu'ang yod phyir them pa'i phyir //
NK014(pha)012:159: nang gi them skas bzhi po 'dzugs //
NK014(pha)012:160: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i rta babs ni //
NK014(pha)012:161: 'degs byed ka ba sgo logs kyi //
NK014(pha)012:162: g.yas g.yon cha phran re re dang //
NK014(pha)012:163: mdun du'ang cha bran gnyis gcig snyam lags /
NK014(pha)012:165: stegs bu gru bzhi cha chung gcig /
NK014(pha)012:166: de steng bum pa'ang tshad de mnyam //
NK014(pha)012:167: brtsegs pas cha chung gnyis pa'i steng //
NK014(pha)012:168: ka ba gzhur bcas cha chung lnga //
NK014(pha)012:169: bsdoms pas dpangs su cha phran bdun //
NK014(pha)012:170: zheng la cha phran gcig ldan pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:171: ka ba phyi ma gnyis po 'dzugs //
NK014(pha)012:172: de dang khad mnyam 'dod snam la //
NK014(pha)012:173: reg pa'i ka ba nang ma gnyis //
NK014(pha)012:174: btsugs pa'i ka ba bzhi po yis //
NK014(pha)012:175: dpangs zheng cha phran re ldan pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:176: gdung sna brgyad btegs rta babs rmang //
NK014(pha)012:177: rgyab gdung dum bu gnyis yin phyir //
NK014(pha)012:178: nang gi gdung sna gnyis pa de //
NK014(pha)012:179: sgo 'gram rtsig pa dag la brten //
NK014(pha)012:180: rgyab mdun gdung gnyis ka ba las //
NK014(pha)012:181: g.yas g.yon cha phran re 'phyar ba //
NK014(pha)012:182: ka rgyan glang seng dag gis btegs //
NK014(pha)012:183: gdung steng rta rkang snam bu ni //
NK014(pha)012:184: mdun snam gdung dang dpangs zheng mnyam //
NK014(pha)012:185: g.yas g.yon zheng la cha chen re //
NK014(pha)012:186: yod phyir ka rgyan mtha' dang mnyam //
NK014(pha)012:187: dkyus su cha bran lnga pa'o //
NK014(pha)012:188: de steng chu skyes dang sgrom gnyis //
NK014(pha)012:189: mdun du sngar dang 'dra ba las //
NK014(pha)012:190: g.yas g.yon cha phran gcig re 'phyar //
NK014(pha)012:191: snam bu de gsum mdun ngos su //
NK014(pha)012:192: so sor re kh+aas bcad pa las //
NK014(pha)012:194: g.yas g.yon mdun gyi snam bu rnams //
NK014(pha)012:195: sgo khang rtsig par cha bran res //
NK014(pha)012:196: ma reg mun pa pa ti'o //
NK014(pha)012:197: snam bu khong stong 'brel khog tu //
NK014(pha)012:198: 'og gi ka thog ka bzhag gi //
NK014(pha)012:199: ka ba bzhi dang sgo logs kyi //
NK014(pha)012:200: rtsig pa'i thad kyi mdun ngos su'ang //
NK014(pha)012:201: ka ba gnyis te drug btsugs pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:202: ka dpangs cha bran gnyis dang ni //
NK014(pha)012:203: thig skud gnyis dang de phyed ldan //
NK014(pha)012:204: de steng gdung dpangs thig skud gang //
NK014(pha)012:205: mdun dang g.yas g.yon khor mor bkab //
NK014(pha)012:206: de steng sgo khang steng gi ni //
NK014(pha)012:207: phyam sne bkal te thog phub pa'i //
NK014(pha)012:208: phyam bcas thog gi 'thug rngams la //
NK014(pha)012:209: thig skud phyed dang gnyis pa'o //
NK014(pha)012:210: sgo khyud g.yas g.yon rtsig thad steng //
NK014(pha)012:211: bya 'dab pu shu mtshon tsam bya //
NK014(pha)012:212: de ltar sgo khang dang ni sgrom //
NK014(pha)012:213: thog rgyun gcig tu gyur pa'i steng //
NK014(pha)012:214: dpangs su cha phran phyed bzhi re //
NK014(pha)012:215: yod pa'i ka ba brgyad po ni //
NK014(pha)012:216: zur bzhir logs kyi rtsig mtha' dang //
NK014(pha)012:217: thad kar phyi ka bzhi po 'dzugs //
NK014(pha)012:218: sgo khyud rtsig pa'i nang mtha' dang //
NK014(pha)012:219: thad mnyam mdun rgyab nang ka bzhi //
NK014(pha)012:220: btsugs pas rgyab ka bzhi po ni //
NK014(pha)012:221: 'gram rtsig phyi dang kha da chad //
NK014(pha)012:222: mdun ka bzhi po rta babs kyi //
NK014(pha)012:223: snam bu'i phyi mtha' las nang du //
NK014(pha)012:224: thig gang dor ba'i nang du'o //
NK014(pha)012:225: ka steng cha phran phyed pa yi //
NK014(pha)012:226: tal gdung bzhi yis gru bzhir phubs //
NK014(pha)012:227: zar tshags sna 'phyong shar bu gsum //
NK014(pha)012:228: ka gdung ngos la sbrags pa ste //
NK014(pha)012:229: spang leb zur langs lta bu yin //
NK014(pha)012:230: chun 'phyang gzhi ma bar stongs la //
NK014(pha)012:231: rin chen sgril ba'i d+r+wa ba 'phyang //
NK014(pha)012:232: gdung steng rgya phubs khyung mgo 'gebs //
NK014(pha)012:233: mdun ngos rta babs bdun khang mnyam //
NK014(pha)012:234: khyung mgo cha bran phyed tsam 'phyar //
NK014(pha)012:235: dpangs ni thams cad cha rer mnyam //
NK014(pha)012:236: g.yas g.yon sgrom las za ra tshags //
NK014(pha)012:237: cha phran gnyis thung de la ni //
NK014(pha)012:238: sna 'phyong cha phran gcig gis ring //
NK014(pha)012:239: de las chun 'phyang gnyis kyis thung //
NK014(pha)012:240: de las shar bu gcig gis ring //
NK014(pha)012:241: de las khyung mgo gcig 'phyar ro //
NK014(pha)012:242: mdun gyi rta babs snam bu rnams //
NK014(pha)012:243: glang rgyab thad kar chad pa yin //
NK014(pha)012:244: de la glang rgyab mig gsum gyi //
NK014(pha)012:245: dbus ma sgrom dang za ra tshags //
NK014(pha)012:247: rta rkang chu skyes gnyis po la //
NK014(pha)012:248: g.yas g.yon mig ste sgrom ma mthar //
NK014(pha)012:249: dbus ma'i mig dang sbrel mtshams 'ong //
NK014(pha)012:250: phyi ma cha chung gcig pa yi //
NK014(pha)012:251: mu ran dag gis mdzes par bya //
NK014(pha)012:252: bar stong zheng la mig dbus ma'i //
NK014(pha)012:253: che sar cha chen gcig pa ste //
NK014(pha)012:254: g.yas g.yon mig gnyis de nyid las //
NK014(pha)012:255: cha bran gnyis re phyir bskyed do //
NK014(pha)012:256: rgya phubs steng dbus pad+ma ni //
NK014(pha)012:257: dpangs su cha gcig zheng la gnyis //
NK014(pha)012:258: chos 'khor cha gnyis gdugs la gcig /
NK014(pha)012:259: pad+ma las ni cha bran phyed //
NK014(pha)012:260: gzhal mthar ri dwags pho mo'i gzugs //
NK014(pha)012:261: cha chung gcig tu mgrin bcas gdong //
NK014(pha)012:263: rta babs glang rgyab do shal nang //
NK014(pha)012:264: pu shu'i kho ra khor yug sogs //
NK014(pha)012:265: phyogs kun gdugs 'phan rgyal mtshan dang //
NK014(pha)012:266: me tog phreng ba sogs kyis brgyan //
NK014(pha)012:267: sgo bzhi re rer glang chen dang //
NK014(pha)012:268: g.yas g.yon ta la'i shing re re //
NK014(pha)012:269: phyogs bzhir dpag bsam ljon shing dang //
NK014(pha)012:270: rin chen 'bar ba'i phung po ni //
NK014(pha)012:271: gnyis gnyis brgyad kyis legs par bkod //
NK014(pha)012:272: rdo rje ra ba'i nang khongs kyi //
NK014(pha)012:273: pad+ma'i lte ba'i kha khyer steng //
NK014(pha)012:274: 'khor lo'i rtsibs rten mu khyud la //
NK014(pha)012:275: lha chen phyogs skyong brgyad la sogs //
NK014(pha)012:276: rang rang mchod yon thogs la 'god //
NK014(pha)012:278: rnam par bzhag pa brjod pa ste //
NK014(pha)012:279: khro dkyil la sogs sgo sbrags dang //
NK014(pha)012:280: bka' brgyad lta bu gcig gi nang //
NK014(pha)012:281: pho brang dgu rdzogs yod pa dang //
NK014(pha)012:283: mtha' dag brjod par mi nus pas //
NK014(pha)012:284: 'di las dpags te shes par bya //
NK014(pha)012:285: de ltar sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba yi //
NK014(pha)012:287: rje btsun bla ma'i dgongs pa bzhin //
NK014(pha)012:289: tshig sbyor spangs te go bder sbyar //
NK014(pha)012:291: sngags pa blo gsar don du'o //
